---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header title={SITE_TITLE} />
		<main>
			<h1>SIM IT Club</h1>
			<p>
				Hi! 👋 Welcome to our little corner of the web. 🌐
			</p>
			<p>
				Here, our goal is to celebrate all things IT 💻,
				and learn crucial IT-related skills needed for the professional world 🌍.
				We frequently organize meetings, talks, workshops, and seminars
				that are open to all students 🎓,
				regardless of their major or level of expertise.
			</p>
			<p>
				We're also a part of the student chapter under the
				Singapore Computer Society (SCS) 🏢
				and
				Association of Information Security Professionals (AISP) 🔐,
			</p>
			<p>
				We're always looking for new members to join us,
				so if you're interested in IT, we'd <a href="https://forms.office.com/Pages/ResponsePage.aspx?id=eF0ERJXMGE2FJ2YvtdVEB-AqdU67K4lKmefPkNg3TaZURVNPNEYyUjRHM0hXS0NBRVg4MVIyR0UzQS4u">love to have you on board!</a> 🚀
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
